<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Origin on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/origin/</link><description>Recent content in Origin on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/origin/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>AWS CloudFront Error: The Request Could Not Be Satisfied (403)</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/aws/cloudfront-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/cloud/aws/cloudfront-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The CloudFront &lt;code&gt;403 Forbidden&lt;/code&gt; error with message &amp;ldquo;The request could not be satisfied&amp;rdquo; occurs when CloudFront rejects a request due to origin access restrictions, origin misconfiguration, or WAF/signed URL requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Origin (S3 bucket or ALB) denies access to CloudFront&amp;rsquo;s IP addresses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Origin Access Control (OAC) or Origin Access Identity (OAI) not configured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CloudFront distribution is associated with a WAF web ACL that blocks the request&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Signed cookies or signed URLs are required but not provided&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The origin bucket policy does not allow the CloudFront distribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check the distribution configuration:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>CORS policy error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/express/cors-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/express/cors-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when a browser blocks a cross-origin request because the Express server&amp;rsquo;s CORS policy does not allow the requesting origin. This is enforced by the browser, not the server.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Origin not included in &lt;code&gt;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&lt;/code&gt; header&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preflight OPTIONS request not handled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Credentials mode (&lt;code&gt;withCredentials&lt;/code&gt;) used with wildcard &lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt; origin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing required CORS headers in the response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the &lt;code&gt;cors&lt;/code&gt; middleware with explicit origins:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cors&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;cors&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cors&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;origin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;http://localhost:3000&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;https://myapp.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;credentials&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle preflight OPTIONS requests:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/api/data&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cors&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set per-route CORS configuration:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/api/public&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cors&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;origin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;*&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; }), (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;req&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;res&lt;/span&gt;) =&amp;gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;res&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;public&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow credentials with specific origins (not &lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt;):&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cors&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;origin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;https://myapp.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;credentials&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;methods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;GET&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;POST&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;PUT&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;DELETE&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Client at http://localhost:3000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fetch&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;http://localhost:5000/api/data&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;credentials&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;include&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Blocked by CORS policy: No &amp;#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&amp;#39; header
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Access to fetch at &amp;#39;http://localhost:5000/api/data&amp;#39; from origin &amp;#39;http://localhost:3000&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;has been blocked by CORS policy: No &amp;#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&amp;#39; header is present
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/express/cannot-set-headers/"&gt;Error: Cannot set headers after they are sent&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>